\faDiamond\ \textlcsc{ \textcolor{dgreen}{\Large \textbf{Study Check}} }\\
Balance the following redox in acidic medium:
\begin{center}\ce{  Cr2O7^{-2}_{(aq)} + NO2^{-}_{(aq)} -> Cr^{3+}_{(aq)} + NO3^-_{(aq)}    }\end{center}
\providetoggle{long}\settoggle{long}{true}\iftoggle{long}{}{\begin{flushright} \mytriangleright{dgreen}\small 
 Answer: \ce{3NO2_{(aq)} + 8H^+_{(aq)} + Cr2O7^{2-}_{(aq)} -> 3NO3^-_{(aq)} + 2Cr^{3+}_{(aq)} + 4H2O_{(l)}}.
 \end{flushright} }
